title: New Jawa 350 launched to compete against Royal Enfield 350, Hunter: Price details, specs and other features
description: Jawa Motorcycles has launched the updated Jawa 350 with a starting price of Rs 2.14 lakh, ex-showroom. The new model features a larger 334 cc engine, six-speed gearbox, assist and slipper clutch, and improved performance. The motorcycle also comes with a new dual-cradle chassis, increased ground clearance, and dual-channel ABS.
